"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Mover</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dica</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
